Package: com.android.build.gradle.internal

[Java] Class SourceSetSourceProviderWrapper

    • com.android.build.gradle.internal.SourceSetSourceProviderWrapper
    • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
      com.android.builder.model.SourceProvider

      public class SourceSetSourceProviderWrapper
extends Object

      An implementation of SourceProvider that's wrapper around a Java SourceSet. This is useful for the case where we store SourceProviders but don't want to query the content of the SourceSet at the moment the SourceProvider is created.
